http://www.typescriptlang.org/Playground/#src=%2F%2F%20comment%0A1%3B%0A%0A%2F*%0A%20*%20comment%0A%20*%2F%0A3%3B

As seen above, 
```
// comment
1;

/*
 * comment
 */
3;
```

is compiled to

```
// comment
// comment
1;

/*
* comment
*/
/*
* comment
*/
3;
```

It should be compiled to

```
// comment
1;

/*
 * comment
 */
3;
```
